column3: Just noticed the typo, lmk if I should resubmit\n
Right - please correct the commit message, just git commit --amend and re-push.\n
I'm not entirely sure about whether we should recommend `make install` though. Is this normal in build documentation?\nMaybe add that it's optional, like the OSX docs.\n
